  "name": "MRLC Data",
  "description": "The Multi-Resolution Land Characteristics (MRLC) Consortium data portal provides nationwide (United States) and North America land cover and related remote-sensing products, including Annual NLCD (annual land cover and land change science products), RCMAP (rangeland fractional cover and trends), Exotic Annual Grass fractional cover products, NALCMS (North American land cover), and legacy NLCD products. The portal also provides tools (e.g., MRLC Viewer, EVA Tool, Rangeland Viewer) and web services (OGC WMS/WCS) for interactive access and subsetting.",
